  <entry>
    <title>sqlite3删除关联的列表行</title>
    <link href="/2021/05/08/sqlite3%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E5%85%B3%E8%81%94%E7%9A%84%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E8%A1%8C/"/>
    <url>/2021/05/08/sqlite3%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E5%85%B3%E8%81%94%E7%9A%84%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E8%A1%8C/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="闲话"><a href="#闲话" class="headerlink" title="闲话"></a>闲话</h2><p>在使用sqlite3删除表里的某一行的时候,需要同时把这个一行在其他的表中对应的行也删除.官网看了半天,也不知道怎么写.</p><p>后面在github的[issues](<a href="https://github.com/sequelize/sequelize/issues/8444">cascade delete does not work · Issue #8444 · sequelize/sequelize (github.com)</a>)中看到了,但不是很好找,所以记录下,方便其他人遇到相同的问题能够找到.</p><h2 id="步骤"><a href="#步骤" class="headerlink" title="步骤"></a>步骤</h2><ol><li>要能够同时删除其他的关联列表行,需要在声明关联关系的时候设置特定的选项.</li></ol><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">User.hasMany(Book, { onDelete: <span class="hljs-string">'CASCADE'</span>, hooks: <span class="hljs-literal">true</span> });<br>Book.belongsTo(<span class="hljs-keyword">User</span>);<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><ol start="2"><li>在使用删除语句的时候,需要先查询,后调用<code>destroy</code></li></ol><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">const <span class="hljs-keyword">user</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> await User.findOne({<br>   <span class="hljs-keyword">where</span>: {<br>     id: <span class="hljs-string">'1394'</span>,<br>   },<br>});<br>await user.destroy();<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
